{
 "file": "_STGX3B.bin",
 "source_size": 36896,
 "built_size": 39764,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x12cd",
   "jp_len": 79,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "あいうえおかダチッツテ{01}デ、トドナ。ネハバ·パ々ビぞブベち{00}·{00}！事{01}Mみすな、{00}{01}！者{00}M{SLOT:1795}な、{00}{01}ぁ来吧、零号机！乖乖跟我们回去！！",
   "zh_hex": "15161718191a1b6566676869016a026b6c6d036f7071047207732975772c00040006a90113fc1e3302000106ad0013a41d3302000115efcfe7d002eb74e833e7e4ef97e9a3e9a3e973efcce7bbef52e7ebef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1337",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们……究竟为何、要对那帮家伙唯命是{00}从！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bb0909e906ef2ce7c1efbc02ef2ae7bee7b7e910e7dfe7fdea89e853e7b600e88aef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x134f",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "被当成兵器、而不是当人来看待、你们就{00}甘心吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f1ef53e837ef93e8c302e89ce7b5e7b6ef53efb2efcfe7f6eaa802e7b8e7bbe7c500ecede82de802ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1388",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们生来、就是为了侍奉加米托夫阁下、{00}作为工具而活！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbef8defcf02e7c5e7b6e7c1e7baeca8eac1e854e878e7f4e830e8d7ef4d0200ef2fe7c1eae4ea14e89ce8d4ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13a9",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "胆敢违抗这一点的你、才是个残次品！",
   "zh_hex": "15edaee8cdeab2e912e7b9efb6e822e7b4e7b802e836e7b6e828e97be864eae1ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13db",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不对！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7beef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13e5",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们是被人施加了精神控制啊！所以……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe7b6e7f1b4eb8de854e7bae98de9aaea3fe8dee7c306e7fbe7f3090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x141b",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……少废话！",
   "zh_hex": "150909efaceae5e81fef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1425",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你若不肯投降、那就只能把你当残次品处{00}分掉了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7e7e7b5e93de948e94302e7b7e7c5ef32e7c6e81be7b8ef53e97be864eae1e90300efaee9d3e7baef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x145f",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……难道只能开战了吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e866e82aef32e7c6e7faef28e7bae802060500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1496",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14b9",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来是被包围了……所谓的逃兵、传闻果{00}然是真的吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcfe7b6e7f1eabbe9dee7ba0909e7fbe92be7b4e8c2ef9302ea38ebace87100e7efe7b6e820e7b4e802090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14f3",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若能与那台MS取得接触、或许能弄到敌{00}方本队的情报",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e7c6e832e7b7ea16efa7ef9ee987e80aefceef4802e905e8a7e7c6eac4e7d7e7e300efb1efa6e7c9e7b4e88be9130000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1512",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "玛利根、MS队出击！去救援那台被包围{00}的MS！",
   "zh_hex": "15e845e82ee9b8021314e7c9afe7cc06e7ebe8cae863e7b7ea16e7f1eabbe9de00e7b4131406000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1553",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那边的MS！别贸然冲到前面去！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e899e7b4efa7ef9eef97e7e5ed08e7efe95ee7d7ef51e862e7ebef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1567",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们马上就赶到你那边！在那之前、你先{00}撑住……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe84fef4ce7c5ea04e7d7e7b8e7b7e899ef97ef29e7b7e7cdef5102e7b8ef8b00ea29e859090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x159c",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不关你们事",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5e8bbe7b8e7bba90000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15c5",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15e7",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我已经不会再听任何人指挥了！{00}别来管我！",
   "zh_hex": "158bef3ae8b7e7b5e7e2e80be8d1e89a8ab4e8c0e949e7ba0600e7e5d9e93b8b06000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1626",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂……我说你这家伙！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd0909efcce7ede7b8e7b9e7dfe7fdef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x164c",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别管我！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e93befccef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x168b",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "前方、新出现了一支敌方部队！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef51efb102ef8aefbee82fe7baefb6e883e7e3efb1ef70e7c9ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16b5",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！没想到他们来得这么快！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97e7d8e7e6e7d7e80ce7bbefcfe80ae7b9e7bde85fef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16ee",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我还在想怎么这么棘手、原来是吉翁军插{00}了一手吗……",
   "zh_hex": "158be7f7ef29e7e6e7f2e7bde7b9e7bded79ae02e8e4d9e7b6e7d9ee88e7e0eb0800e7ba87aee80209090000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x170c",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "绝不能把零号、交到那帮家伙手里！",
   "zh_hex": "15e91ce7b5e7c6e81beb74e83302e861e7d7e7b7e910e7dfe7fdaeef3106000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1725",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全舰、开始攻击！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e7d402e7fae908ef67e7ccef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1758",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "又是你……我不是说了别来管我吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8f1e7b6e7b80909efcce7b5e7b6e7ede7bae7e5efcfe93befcce802ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x178e",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "眼睁睁看着有人在面前遭联邦军攻击、我{00}怎能坐视不管！",
   "zh_hex": "15e90bed90ed90e7f6e86de7cbefb2ef29e862ef51eb1eef2eefaae7e0ef67e7cc02efcc00e7f2e7c6ecc3e9d9e7b5e93bef97000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17cd",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我已经不会再听任何人指挥了！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef3ae8b7e7b5e7e2e80be8d1e89aefbcefb2e8c0e949e7baef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17e0",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要是再在我眼前晃来晃去、连你们也一起{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b6e80bef29efcce90bef51ec20efcfec20e7eb02e86ee7b8e7bbe7c0efb6e8470009090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1818",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好了好了、你们两个！在这儿自相残杀又{00}有什么意义？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e7bae7c7e7ba02e7b8e7bbe97de828ef97ef29e7b9eb7cefb5e8b1e97be89be8f100e7cbe7dde7bdef3ce8ce05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1856",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……西玛中佐？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7f8e845ef4eefba05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x187b",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌人的敌人就是友军……虽说也未必尽然",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb2e7b4e7e3efb2e7c5e7b6e960e7e00909e8b8e7ede7c0e8b4e860e8f2e7ef000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1893",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但联邦是敌人这一点、你和我们都是一样{00}的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbef2eefaae7b6e7e3efb2e7b9efb6e82202e7b8e7d3efcce7bbe840e7b6efb6e7da00e7b400000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18c6",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18ea",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总之、暂且联手一下而已、应该没什么不{00}行的吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e7cd02e9ffe999ef2eef66efb6ef4de89cef3a02e873e898e7d8e7dde7bde7b500efd6e7b4e7d0050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1925",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……好吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c7e7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x192f",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、有句话先说在前头、别妨碍我就行",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e7cbebb9e81fef8be7edef29ef51e92e02e7e5e97fe8c6efcce7c5efd60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1948",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还有、我也不会听你们指挥、我要按自己{00}的方式来",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7cb02efcce7c0e7b5e7e2e8d1e7b8e7bbe8c0e94902efccef2aea76efb5e8c900e7b4efb1ea26efcf00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1990",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛……总之、能拉起一条共同战线、就已{00}经算不错了",
   "zh_hex": "15e9360909e881e7cd02e7c6e7c2e84787e9d4ea48e85def28e91602e7c5ef3a00e8b7e889e7b5e885e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19cb",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "西玛中佐……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f8e845ef4eefba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19f9",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是我多管闲事了吗？不过、我就是有那么{00}点在意",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6efcce7e9e93beebeefb8e7bae80205e7b5ef3602efcce7c5e7b6e7cbe7b7e7bd00e822ef29ef3c00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a16",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那种固执的样子啊、简直就像在看当{00}年的我们",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7d1eac0e9fce7b4e7dae886e7c302e9abe875e7c5e8e9ef29e7f6ef5300e909e7b4efcce7bb0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a50",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "能这么一笑置之、看来你也变得随和多了{00}啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c6e7b9e7bdefb6ea1cea0ee7cd02e7f6efcfe7b8e7c0e955e80ae9a1e7d3e7e9e7ba00e7c3000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a8a",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛……托某人的福",
   "zh_hex": "15e9360909e7f4eae8efb2e7b4ea7c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ab6",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……多谢",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7e9e8b2000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aef",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你、你……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b802e7b809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b1e",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、头好痛……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e92ee7c7ea0b0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b48",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这感觉……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e87de8ae0909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b56",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "难道说、你也和我一样……",
   "zh_hex": "15e866e82ae7ed02e7b8e7c0e7d38b87e7da09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b80",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……咦？这、这是什么……{00}到底怎么回事！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef4905e7b902e7b9e7b6e7dde7bd090900e7d7e9b4e7f2e7bd8ca9060500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b95",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我这头怎么会这么痛！？{00}还有、你又是……",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b9e92ee7f2e7bde7e2e7b9e7bdea0b060500e7f7e7cb02e7b8e8f1e7b609090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bd3",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是吗……你什么都不知道啊、那、就这样{00}一直不知情、或许反而更好",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8020909e7b8e7dde7bde840e7b5e85ae82ae7c302e7b702e7c5e7b9e7da0087e875e7b5e85ae88b02e905e8a7e87ce89ce952e7c70000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c30",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "本想就这样、找个谁都不在的地方、静静{00}地消失……",
   "zh_hex": "15efa6e7e6e7c5e7b9e7da02e9d2e828e923e840e7b5ef29e7b4ef63efb102eab3eab300ef63e928e8a509090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c4e",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……可在见到你之后、这份决心却动摇了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c4ef29e85ce7d7e7b8e7cde7fe02e7b9ea22e8abe82deadfef30ebcce7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c85",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请让我来守护你",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae7f9efccefcfe8a8e8e0e7b800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cb3",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b80909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cd6",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "绝不能再让……像你我这般不幸的人、继{00}续增多下去",
   "zh_hex": "15e91ce7b5e7c6e80be7f90909e8e9e7b8efcce7b9ea80e7b5ea8de7b4efb202e9d600e9adea3de7e9ef4de7eb0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d15",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d1e",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为什么呢……明明你说的话、我都听不懂{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7dde7bde9070909ef39ef39e7b8e7ede7b4e81f02efcce840e8d1e7b5e8b0000909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d3f",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可我……却想试着去相信你……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4efcc0909eadfe7e6e91de86de7ebe8b1e90fe7b80909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d76",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是零·村雨……你叫什么名字？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6eb74ef4beb8eebad0909e7b8e8c1e7dde7bde8ace9800500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1da6",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我叫蕾拉……蕾拉·雷蒙德",
   "zh_hex": "158be8c1e84ce7c20909e84ce7c204e8afe942e82c00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ddb",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蕾拉……我一定会保护好你的！",
   "zh_hex": "15e84ce7c20909efccefb6e867e7e2ea47e8e0e7c7e7b8e7b4ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e1b",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这、这感觉……对方是新人类吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b902e7b9e87de8ae0909e7beefb1e7b6ef8aefb2e841e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e33",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e55",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们是天选的新人类！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b6e844e966e7b4ef8aefb2e841ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e65",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我倒要让你见识见识、和你这种半吊子新{00}人类的不同！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce848ef2ae7f9e7b8e85ce92fe85ce92f02e7d3e7b8e7b9e7d1eadeed31e886ef8a00efb2e841e7b4e7b5e85def9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1eaf",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你那台MS……真的是联邦的机体吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b7ea16efa7ef9e0909e820e7b4e7b6ef2eefaae7b4e7e4ef4fe8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ec6",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那外形、怎么看都不像是联邦制造的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8f7ec6702e7f2e7bde7f6e840e7b5e8e9e7b6ef2ed1e8dee93ee7b40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ef8",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "呵呵……这可是你们吉翁、曾经开发的新{00}型机",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3def3d0909e7b9e7c4e7b6e7b8e7bbe7d9ee8802ea2ae8b7e7fae870e7b4ef8a00e977e7e400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f2e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "果然……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e871e7ef0909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f52",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这等性能……给你们用实在太浪费了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e826e951e7c60909e839e7b8e7bbd8e87fef29e86aed81e95de7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f69",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只有我们才配用！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32e7cbefcce7bbe836ea34efb3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f97",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "投靠联邦的那副模样……我实在看不下去{00}至少、由我亲手送你上路！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e948e8c7ef2ed1e7b4e7b7ecb6ea91e7da09098be87fef29e7f6e7b589e7eb00e897b102e8a68be894aee9bae7b8b2e8d2060600000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fe7",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！什么！？头好痛……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d090906e7dde7bd0605e92ee7c7ea0b0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2026",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是吗……你也和我们是同类吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8020909e7b8e7c0e7d3efcce7bbe7b6e85de841e802000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x203a",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但说到底、也只是吉翁货色、根本不是我{00}们的对手！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbe7ede7d7e9b402e7c0ef32e7b6e7d9ee88eaf5e89f02e9b8d2e7b5e7b68b00e7bbe7b4e7beae06000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2071",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什、什么！？你们到底在说些什么啊！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dd02e7dde7bdef9705e7b8e7bbe7d7e9b4ef29e7ede8a4e7dde7bde7c3ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20ae",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bb09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20d2",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟能感知到我们的存在……原来如此、你{00}也是个新人类吗",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7c6e87de85ae7d7efcce7bbe7b4e993ef290909e8e4efcfe7f0e7ca02e7b800e7c0e7b6e828ef8aefb2e841e8020000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x210b",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……你们、根本就不是新人类……",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b8e7bb02e9b8efa6e7c5e7b5e7b6ef8aefb2e841090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2121",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我确实能感觉到力量……但那股力量、并{00}不自然……",
   "zh_hex": "158be88ce87fe7c6e87de8aee7d7dae8510909e7dbe7b7edacdae85102e95700e7b5abe7ef090900000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2159",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "胡说！我们才是真正的新人类！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec8be7edef97efcce7bbe836e7b6e820ef3be7b4ef8aefb2e841ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2195",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21c3",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不好！玛利根、快去救那名驾驶员……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7c706e845e82ee9b802e85fe7ebe8cae7b7e8ace953e975e84909090600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21f9",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bb090906050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2204",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "住手！我……",
   "zh_hex": "15e859ef66ef97efcc09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2244",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "都什么时候了还说这种话！再这样下去你{00}会死的！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e840e7dde7bdef2dea39e7bae7f7e7ede7b9e7d1e81fef97e80be7b9e7daef4de7ebe7b800e7e2ef6ae7b4ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x225f",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "玛利根！把那名驾驶员救回来！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e845e82ee9b806e81be7b7e8ace953e975e849e8ca8cd9060600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x228c",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22b7",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "驾驶员收容好了吗……那就只剩敌方部队{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15e953e975e849e926ed2fe7c7e7bae8020909e7b7e7c5ef32ea3ae7e3d0cce7c900e7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22cf",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全机、把敌方部队驱逐出去！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e7e402e81be7e3efb1ef70e7c9ebffec9cefbee7ebef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2303",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚大佐！敌方部队已成功驱逐！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6efa5efbaef97e7e3efb1ef70e7c9ef3ae837e9b1ebffec9cef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2334",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好、干得漂亮、接下来……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c702e8d3e80aead0eaa202efceef4defcf090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x236d",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "强化人吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ade9a5efb2e8020909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2393",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "联邦就是这么称呼那些被人工制造出来的{00}新人类的",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2eefaae7c5e7b6e7b9e7bdea01ea3ce7b7e8a4e7f1efb2eae4e8dee93eefbeefcfe7b400ef8aefb2e841e7b400000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23cd",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那就是你吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7c5e7b6e7b8e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23f2",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "村雨研究所的试作一号新人类、原型·零{00}……那就是我",
   "zh_hex": "15eb8eebadea0ce906e7fbe7b4e91def2f87e833ef8ab4e84102e8e4e97704eb74000909e7b7e7c5e7b68b0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x242d",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "人工制造的新人类吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb2eae4e8dee93ee7b4ef8aefb2e841e802090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2457",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、你……今后打算怎么办？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7b80909efb9e7fee7f5e889e7f2e7bde8ea0500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2470",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "既然是从联邦逃出来的、应该是不打算回{00}军队了吧……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c4e7efe7b6e88aef2eefaae8c2efbeefcfe7b402e873e898e7b6e7b5e7f5e889ef5200e7e0e7c9e7bae7d0090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24af",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我也不知道",
   "zh_hex": "1509098be7c0e7b5e85ae82a000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24b9",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为不愿被当成兵器、我才冲出了部队、{00}可是……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c1e7b5e961e7f1ef53e837ef93e8c302efcce836e95eefbee7baef70e7c90200e7c4e7b609090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24d8",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没想过之后的事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e7e6ef36e7cde7fee7b4efb8000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2505",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、要来阿克西斯吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02ef2aefcfe7d2e7d5e7f8e7c8e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2534",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "然后把我当成研究材料、交给吉翁的新人{00}类研究机构吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7efe7fee81b8bc4e837ea0ce906ebcfeb8c02e861e839e7d9ee88e7b4ef8ab400e841ea0ce906e7e4ece3e80205000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2585",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们绝不会那么做！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe91ce7b5e7e2e7b7e7bde81cef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25ac",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈曼！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e874ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25d8",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "被当成研究的材料、究竟是一件多么痛苦{00}的事……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f1ef53e837ea0ce906e7b4ebcfeb8c02e906ef2ce7b6efb6e991e7e9e7bdea0be9e600e7b4efb809090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25f5",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一直被那样对待过来的我、最是清楚不过",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e875e7f1e7b7e7dae7beeaa8ef36efcfe7b4efcc02e8c5e7b6e995ebd3e7b5ef3600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x260e",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以……我绝对不会让那种事发生！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f30909efcce91ce7bee7b5e7e2e7f9e7b7e7d1efb8e870ef8def9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x263e",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2660",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是哈曼·卡恩……和你一样、是个新人{00}类",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e7e8e874ef4be801e7ee0909e7d3e7b8efb6e7da02e7b6e828ef8aefb200e841000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2693",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、我……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502efcc0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26b9",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们同样都是新人类、对吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe85de7dae840e7b6ef8aefb2e84102e7bee7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26c7",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "同为新人类……我们之间、应该能够相互{00}理解才对吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e85de7c1ef8aefb2e8410909efcce7bbe7cde8fc02e873e898e7c6e920e8b1e9f900e872e89de836e7bee7d00500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26ff",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2723",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "能不能相信我们？绝不会亏待你",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c6e7b5e7c6e8b1e90fefcce7bb05e91ce7b5e7e2eab7eaa8e7b80000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x275f",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿克西斯的胸怀、比你想象的要宽广得多",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e7d5e7f8e7c8e7b4ee8ceb0302e825e7b8e7e6ebf2e7b4ef2aed4cee17e80ae7e90000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x277c",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "臭名远扬的西玛舰队、连我们这样的人、{00}阿克西斯都肯收留",
   "zh_hex": "15ecfde8ace94cebc6e7b4e7f8e845e7d4e7c902e86eefcce7bbe7b9e7dae7b4efb20200e7d2e7d5e7f8e7c8e840e93de926e98c00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x279b",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你的容身之处、也一定能找得到……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b4ed2fe88de7cde90302e7c087e867e7c6e9d2e80ae7d7090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27c9",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……说得对、如果是你们……或许可以相{00}信",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7ede80ae7be02e7f0e871e7b6e7b8e7bb0909e905e8a7e7c4e7f3e8b100e90f00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2800",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……谢谢你",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8b2e8b2e7b80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2807",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请让我重新欢迎你的加入、我是夏亚·阿{00}兹纳布尔",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae7f9efcce8a1ef8aea92e931e7b8e7b4e854e89102efcce7b6ef37e7d6ef4be7d200e856e882e831e7e10000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x283e",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我是零·村雨",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7b6eb74ef4beb8eebad0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x286a",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "零·村雨吗……还请多多关照",
   "zh_hex": "15eb74ef4beb8eebade8020909e7f7e83ae7e9e7e9e8bbea1a000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2893",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……零",
   "zh_hex": "150909eb740000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28b5",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蕾拉！？你怎么会在这种地方……难道说{00}！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e84ce7c20605e7b8e7f2e7bde7e2ef29e7b9e7d1bfd00909e866e82ae7ed00060500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28e6",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯、你们说的话……我都听到了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86502e7b8e7bbe7ede7b4e81f0909efcce840e8d1e7d7e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2922",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、你……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7b809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2947",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你和我是一样的……刚才、你是这么说的{00}吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7d3efcce7b6efb6e7dae7b40909e8bce83602e7b8e7b6e7b9e7bde7ede7b400e7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2963",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我也是强化人吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c0e7b6e8ade9a5efb2e80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x298a",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29ae",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂、告诉我！我、想了解我自己啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd02e8e5ead6efccef97efcc02e7e6e7bae89defccefb5e8c9e7c3ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29e4",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我并不确定",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce957e7b5e88ce8670000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29ee",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我没有确证……只是、我能感应到你……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7d8e7cbe88ceba30909ef32e7b602efcce7c6e87de873e7d7e7b8090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a0b",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "大概……我猜你是吉翁的强化人……",
   "zh_hex": "15beec7609098bee65e7b8e7b6e7d9ee88e7b4e8ade9a5b409090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a3c",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是吗……原来我并不是真正的新人类啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e8020909e8e4efcfefcce957e7b5e7b6e820ef3be7b4ef8aefb2e841e7c30000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a70",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蕾拉……对不起",
   "zh_hex": "15e84ce7c20909e7bee7b5e8470000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a97",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你不用道歉",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b5d8e82ae9270000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2aa6",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再说、就算知道自己是强化人、我也不觉{00}得难过",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7ed02e7c5e889e85ae82aabe8c9e7b6e8ade9a5b4028be7c0e7b5e8ae00e80ae866ef36000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ae4",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "蕾拉……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e84ce7c20909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b08",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "因为、我并不孤单……有同是强化人的你{00}、在我身边",
   "zh_hex": "15ef33e7c102efcce957e7b5eac2e9180909e7cbe85de7b6e8ade9a5efb2e7b4e7b80002ef29efcce88de899000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b29",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……对吧？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7bee7d00500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b50",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e865ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b58",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我……不、我绝不会让你伤心难过！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc0909e7b502efcce91ce7b5e7e2e7f9e7b8e8f9e82de866ef36ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b71",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后我会一直守护着你！……我向你保证{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7feefcce7e2efb6e875e8a8e8e0e86de7b8ef970909efccefc1e7b8ea47eba300ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ba4",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你……零",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b80909eb740000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x70d6",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不好！要是本营被攻陷、那可就糟了……{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7c706ef2ae7b6d2ed01e7f19eeaf902e7b7e7c4e7c5eeafe7ba090900060600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x711e",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "话说回来、火星那头、真的会有吉翁军吗{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81fe7ed8cd902e8dab5e7b7e92e02e820e7b4e7e2e7cbe7d9ee88e7e0e80200050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7153",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这次远征、究竟花掉了多少预算啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e864e94cecd202e906ef2ceb9fe9d3e7bae7e9efacea5ae889e7c309090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x716e",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "去了之后却以失败收场、那可交代不过去{00}啊、准将？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7ebe7bae7cde7feeadfe7f3e8a5e88fe926e87602e7b7e7c4e861e8e7e7b5ef36e7eb00e7c302e87ae84a05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71aa",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71ce",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你在听吗、准将！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef29e8d1e80202e87ae84a060500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x71fa",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好了好了、各位、请别这么急着发火嘛",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7e7bae7c7e7ba02e819e83402e83ae7e5e7b9e7bdea62e86de870e8dae9360000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x722e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿兹拉埃尔理事……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e856e7c2e96ae7e1e872efb809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7252",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正因为加米托夫准将有十足把握、才会派{00}出远征军……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3bef33e7c1e854e878e7f4e830e87ae84ae7cbea4aea1ee81beb3702e836e7e2e98500afe94cecd2e7e009090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x726d",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……对吧、准将？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7bee7d002e87ae84a050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7295",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "吉翁残党军固守在小行星带、这确实是不{00}争的事实……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d9ee88e97bea73e7e0eac0e8a8ef29e83e9fb5e93702e7b9e88ce87fe7b6e7b500e852e7b4a9e87f0909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x72d2",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "而且还有情报称、他们正为进攻地球而加{00}紧扩充军备",
   "zh_hex": "15e89ce999e7f7e7cbe88be913ea0102e80ce7bbef3be7c1e892ef67ef63efd3e89ce85400eaedec1aea86e7e0e87700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7317",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7320",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来宇宙居民、净是些不肯死心的家伙",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcfe8bee8bfea4cef3802ecb0e7b6e8a4e7b5e93def6ae82de7b4e7dfe7fd0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x733c",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对吧、各位？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7bee7d002e819e834050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7364",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哪怕只是边境的一角、也绝不容许吉翁残{00}党的军事据点存在",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ffe958ef32e7b6e899eb81e7b487eb1a02e7c0e91ce7b5ed2fe8a7e7d9ee88e97b00ea73e7b4e7e0a9e8cce822e993ef29000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7386",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也是为了将宇宙居民的反抗、消灭在源头{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7b6e7c1e7bae84ae8bee8bfea4cef38e7b4e87ce91202e928e8e1ef29ebd6e92e000909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x739f",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唯有坚决彻底地、将其一举歼灭！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea89e7cbeb80e8abebc5e9b4ef6302e84ae8cfefb6ea21eaafe8e1ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x73ca",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是内应吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e99ae873e80209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x73ee",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "袭击马哈拉贾提督的那等手法……绝不可{00}能是偶然的遭遇",
   "zh_hex": "15e9aee7cce84fe7e8e7c2e9e8e821ea1be7b4e7b7e826ef66e84e0909e91ce7b5e7c400e7c6e7b6ea85e7efe7b4eb1eea43000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x742b",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "来者不拒的提督方针、反倒成了祸根吗…{00}…",
   "zh_hex": "15efcfef6ee7b5eb07e7b4e821ea1befb1ebf802e87ce848e837e7baec30e9b8e802090009000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7464",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总之、必须尽快展开内部侦查",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e7cd02e860e9a2e8f2e85fe989e7fae99aef70eeeaeae9000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7498",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那件事就交给我来处理吧……不过、前提{00}是还来得及",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e991efb8e7c5e861e839efccefcfe903e872e7d00909e7b5ef3602ef51e82100e7b6e7f7efcfe80ae9cf00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x74ce",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "事态紧急、必须赶在敌方本队抵达阿克西{00}斯之前……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb8e994eaedea6202e860e9a2ea04ef29e7e3efb1efa6e7c9e96eef2be7d2e7d5e7f800e7c8e7cdef5109090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x751f",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哈斯勒提督！！联、联邦军他们……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e8e7c8e9cee821ea1bef97ef97ef2e02ef2eefaae7e0e80ce7bb0909ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7558",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7579",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "被抢了先手吗……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f1ebc8e7baef8bef66e8020909ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x75a3",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚大佐！请立刻派出迎击部队！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6efa5efbaef97e83ae86be91fe985efbee931e7ccef70e7c9ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x75d3",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "明白！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef39e809ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x75f2",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？你说联邦军打过来了！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef9705e7b8e7edef2eefaae7e0e7f5ef36efcfe7baef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7622",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶、联邦军这帮家伙！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de02ef2eefaae7e0e7b9e910e7dfe7fdef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x762f",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我不是早就说过了吗！！早该再次进攻地{00}球的！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b5e7b6e963e7c5e7edef36e7bae802ef97ef97e963e898e80be864e892ef67ef6300efd3e7b4ef97ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7668",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "队长！我们、真打得赢吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c9ef34ef97efcce7bb02e820e7f5e80ae9cbe802ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x767e",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不是说敌人是一支大军吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7b6e7ede7e3efb2e7b6efb6e883efa5e7e0e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7691",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们这边、连战备都还没整顿好呢……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b9e89902e86eef28e877e840e7f7e7d8e9feedc7e7c7e90709090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x76cb",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "马哈拉贾提督要是能再争气一点就好了…{00}…！",
   "zh_hex": "15e84fe7e8e7c2e9e8e821ea1bef2ae7b6e7c6e80be852e8edefb6e822e7c5e7c7e7ba090009ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7704",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "就是说啊！！都怪上层太不像话了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c5e7b6e7ede7c3ef97ef97e840ea07ef4cebc1e86ae7b5e8e9e81fe7baef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x771a",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "说到底、我们会沦落到这种角落里苦撑、{00}还不都是因为……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7ede7d7e9b402efcce7bbe7e2ece5e92ae7d7e7b9e7d1eb1ae92aef31e9e6ea290200e7f7e7b5e840e7b6ef33e7c10909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7769",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啥！？",
   "zh_hex": "15eabeef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7772",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个夏亚大佐、竟把基西莉亚阁下……！{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e828ef37e7d6efa5efba02ef2ce81be829e7f8e81ee7d6e8d7ef4d0909ef970005000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x77a7",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7beef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x77ae",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "要不是出了那档子事、阿·巴瓦·库一役{00}、本该是我们获胜的！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ae7b5e7b6efbee7bae7b7ed78e886efb802e7d2ef4be85be99fef4be9b3efb6ed590002efa6e898e7b6efcce7bbe9d8e8dbe7b4ef970000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x77d3",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "连那样的夏亚大佐都肯接纳、如今的上层{00}、还信得过吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e86ee7b7e7dae7b4ef37e7d6efa5efbae840e93defcee88202e7f0efb9e7b4ef4cebc10002e7f7e90fe80aef36e802ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x77f0",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们说是吧、各位！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe7ede7b6e7d002e819e834ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x785e",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路辛苦了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ea58e9e6e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x786b",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你、将这条『宇宙世纪路线』一直玩{00}到了最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b802e84ae7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb6e875e97000e7d7e7bae8c5e7fe0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x788b",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的战斗、就先在此告{00}一段落了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ef28e7ff02e7c5ef8bef29e7cae8e500efb6ea6be92ae7ba0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x78aa",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "游戏本身仍然可以继续、今后也请继续尽{00}情享受",
   "zh_hex": "15ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7efe7c4e7f3e9d6e9ad02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae9d6e9ade8f200e88bec06e8c80000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x78cf",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、为将本路线一直玩到最后的你、还{00}准备了特别关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702e7c1e84aefa6e8d2e916efb6e875e970e7d7e8c5e7fee7b4e7b802e7f700e87ae877e7bae7cfe7e5e8bbe80100000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x78f6",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头、一直另行作战的大天使{00}队的特别演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e832efcce7bbefaee92e02efb6e875e99befd6ef2fef28e7b4efa5e844e83f00e7c9e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7917",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "与他们一战、检验一下你一路培养起来的{00}部队实力、也未尝不可",
   "zh_hex": "15e832e80ce7bbefb6ef2802ee40ea99efb6ef4de7b8efb6e8d2edfeec0be847efcfe7b400ef70e7c9e87fefb002e7c0e8b4eccfe7b5e7c40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x793c",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特殊演习』、便可与{00}他们一战",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29abe8a6e7beef28c0e966eaaa0ce7cfed7bea2feab60d02e8fae7c4e83200e80ce7bb87ef280000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7961",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7985",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也希望你、慢慢地尽情玩到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e87be965e7b802e979e979ef63e8f2e88be970e7d7e8c5e7fe0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x79fe",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你、一直陪着我这样一个靠不住的舰{00}长走到现在",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b802efb6e875ef42e86defcce7b9e7daefb6e828e8c7e7b5e859e7b4e7d400ef34e890e7d7e82fef290000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a1d",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』、就到此告一段落{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae8e5efb6ea6be92a00e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a3b",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说、我们预防者的战斗、已经到此结束{00}了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ed02efcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4ef28e7ff02ef3ae8b7e7d7e7cae868e89500e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a55",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身还可以继续玩哦、今后也请{00}你继续尽情享受",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88de7f7e7c4e7f3e9d6e9ade970e91902efb9e7fee7c0e83a00e7b8e9d6e9ade8f2e88bec06e8c80000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a7b",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为将这条路线一直玩到最后的你、还准备{00}了新的关卡哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e84ae7b9e9d4e8d2e916efb6e875e970e7d7e8c5e7fee7b4e7b802e7f7e87ae87700e7baef8ae7b4e8bbe801e9190000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7a9f",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头、一直在和提坦斯、新吉{00}翁作战的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e8328be7bbcde92e0287e875ef29e7d3e821e843e7c802ef8ae7d900ee88ef2fef28e7b40909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7aba",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……与隆德·贝尔队的特别演习哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6e9190000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7acd",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能和{00}他们交战哦",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e7d300e80ce7bbe861ef28e91900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7af3",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请务必挑战",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae94fe860eae7ef28000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b01",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7b25",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自由对战的战火！冲锋吧、大天使号！{00}！』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5e8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97e95ee967e7d002efa5e844e83fe833ef9700ef970d000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ba6",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号的舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露{00}中佐",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7b4e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e85800ef4eefba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7bb6",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、请允许我向你一路以来出色的指挥{00}、致以敬意",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802e83aecade8a78b9de7b887e8d2e7f3d9afe89fe7b4e8c0e9490002ea32e7f3ee38ef3c000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7bd8",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多亏了你的协力、我们才得以一直奋战到{00}最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9eab7e7bae7b8e7b4e8f6efb002efcce7bbe836e80ae7f3efb6e875ef46ef28e7d700e8c5e7fe0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7bfa",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』、就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c10",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说、我们主天使队的战斗、已经到此结{00}束……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ed02efcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4ef28e7ff02ef3ae8b7e7d7e7cae86800e8950909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c29",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "游戏本身仍然可以继续、今后也请继续尽{00}情享受",
   "zh_hex": "15ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7efe7c4e7f3e9d6e9ad02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae9d6e9ade8f200e88bec06e8c8000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c4d",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战今后仍可继续、另外、只要选择{00}『特别演习』……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28efb9e7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e99be8f702ef32ef2ae966eaaa000ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c78",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还能与隆德·贝尔、预防者进行联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7c6e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e102ea5ae968ef6ee892efd6ef2eefc0ea2feab60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7c96",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我相信、以你的实力、与他们一战也定能{00}取胜",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8b1e90f02e7f3e7b8e7b4e87fefb002e832e80ce7bbefb6ef28e7c0e867e7c600e987e8db000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7cbb",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7cdf",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也祝你武运长久",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0ed97e7b8e8ece986ef34e9db00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d06",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……唔！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e81def9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d0e",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这感觉？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e87de8ae050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d3e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是从那台MS传来的吗……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e88ae7b7ea16efa7ef9eea38efcfe7b4e8020909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7d72",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7da7",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……蕾拉少尉！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e84ce7c2efacefc6ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7dda",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是谁……？驾驶那台MS的人、究竟是…{00}…？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e923090905e953e975e7b7ea16efa7ef9ee7b4efb202e906ef2ce7b60900090500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7df5",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不知道……明明应该是个不认识的人……{00}可我……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e85ae82a0909ef39ef39e873e898e7b6e828e7b5e8a0e92fe7b4b4090900e7c48b0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e43",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "走掉了……那家伙怎么了？",
   "zh_hex": "15e890e9d3e7ba0909e7b7e7dfe7fde7f2e7bde7ba05000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e70",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我也不清楚、不过、蕾拉少尉同样是{00}个新人类",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7c0e7b5e995ebd302e7b5ef3602e84ce7c2efacefc6e85de7dae7b600e828ef8aefb2e8410000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7e88",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "她或许是从那台MS的驾驶员身上、感应{00}到了什么",
   "zh_hex": "15e88ee905e8a7e7b6e88ae7b7ea16efa7ef9ee7b4e953e975e849e88def4c02e87de87300e7d7e7bae7dde7bd000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ea4",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们也追上去！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7c0e8ddef4ce7ebef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ed6",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我知道",
   "zh_hex": "1509098be85ae82a000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ee1",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说只是结果使然、但你们救了我、这是{00}事实",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7edef32e7b6e868e871e83fe7ef02e7dbe7b8e7bbe8cae7baefcc02e7b9e7b600efb8e87f00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7efc",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我这边的情况、多少会跟你们说一说的",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b9e899e7b4e88be8d002e7e9eface7e2e973e7b8e7bbe7edefb6e7ede7b4000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f26",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你能这么说、我很感激、那么……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7c6e7b9e7bde7ed02efcce981e87de9b902e7b7e7bd0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f3b",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "玛利根、西玛中佐！目的既已达成、就不{00}必再久留了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e845e82ee9b802e7f8e845c0a306d5e7b4e8c4ef3aef2be83702e7c5e7b500e860e80be9dbe98ce7ba0600000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f58",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "MS一收容完毕、就离开这里！",
   "zh_hex": "15131487e926ed2fe87eea2c02e7c5e901e7fae7b9ef310600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f92",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……",
   "zh_hex": "150909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7f9b",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "本不打算再和吉翁军扯上关系、可情况变{00}了",
   "zh_hex": "15d2e7b5e7f5e889e80be7d3e7d9ee88e7e0ed62b2e8bbe94102e7c4e88be8d0e95500e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7fd1",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是……关于蕾拉少尉的事吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b60909e8bbe879e84ce7c2efacefc6e7b4efb8e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ffb",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不想让她听到",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5e7e6e7f9e88ee8d1e7d70000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8027",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我明白了、那就另外安排一个谈话的{00}机会吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909efccef39e809e7ba02e7b7e7c5e99be8f7e7fcea67efb6e828eaf4e81fe7b400e7e4e7e2e7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8041",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这样可以吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7dae7c4e7f3e7d0050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8066",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "…明白",
   "zh_hex": "1509ef39e8090000"
  }
 ]
}
